org.hibernate.envers.entities.mapper.relation

Class MiddleIdData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.envers.entities.mapper.relation.MiddleIdData

  • public final class MiddleIdData
extends Object
    A class holding information about ids, which form a virtual "relation" from a middle-table. Middle-tables are used when mapping collections.
